gw.lang

Class RpcWebService

  • gw.lang.RpcWebService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAnnotation, IDeclarationSiteValidator, _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject, WebServiceClassAnnotation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WebService

    public class RpcWebService
implements IAnnotation, WebServiceClassAnnotation, IDeclarationSiteValidator, _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    The @RpcWebService annotation is used to expose a class as an RPC/Encoded web service. The preferred way to expose a web service, however, is to use the @WsiWebService annotation instead.
